  "rage-active": false,
  "notes": "--- Planned Progression ---\nPlanned Progression: Sha'ir 3 -> LA Buyback -> Durthan 2 -> Sand Shaper 10 -> Durthan 7\n\nNeed: Know (Nature) 4, Survival 4, Touchstone (City of the Dead) (Needs Know(Local - City of the Dead) 8, or possession of a touchstone key (a portable object native to the area worth at least 250 gp). must also forge a link by spending a day in meditation and spending 10 xp and 250 gp in material components; alternatively, the key object can be destroyed as part of the ritual, in place of the material component)\n\nFlaws: Hot-Blooded (Automatically fail Fort saves made to overcome the effects of low temperatures. Cold-based effects deal an additional 2 points of damage to you), Material Devotion (You may only use spell-trigger items (wands and staffs) that cast spells on your domain spell lists. Other spell-trigger items fail in your hands)\n\nTraits: Honest (+1 Diplo, -1 Bluff, Sense Motive), Polite (+1 Diplo, -2 Intimidate)\n\nSpell Retrieval:\nModifiers to Diplomacy Check (Base DC 20):\n+1 per sha'ir level\n+2 for known arcane spell\n-2 per level of spell\n-6 for unknown divine spell\n-1 per +1 lvl from metamagic\n-2 per attempt after a failed check (resets the next day)\n\nDelay:\n-Known Arcane Spell: d4+ spell level rounds\n-Unknown Arcane Spell: d6+ spell level minutes\n-Divine Spell: d6 + spell level hours",
